trans-unit.source: Represents a reference to a method.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en referanse til en annen metode.

trans-unit.source: A CodeMethodReferenceExpression can be used to represent an expression of the form Object.Method.
trans-unit.target: En CodeMethodReferenceExpression kan brukes til å representere et uttrykk av skjemaet objekt.metode.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMethodReferenceExpression.TargetObject%2A> property indicates the object that contains the method.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMethodReferenceExpression.TargetObject%2A>egenskapen angir objektet som inneholder metoden.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMethodReferenceExpression.TargetObject%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMethodReferenceExpression.MethodName%2A> property indicates the name of the method.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMethodReferenceExpression.MethodName%2A>egenskapen angir navnet på metoden.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMethodReferenceExpression.MethodName%2A>

trans-unit.source: A CodeMethodReferenceExpression is used with a <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMethodInvokeExpression> to indicate the method to invoke, and with a <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeDelegateCreateExpression> to indicate the method to handle the event.
trans-unit.target: En CodeMethodReferenceExpression brukes med en <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMethodInvokeExpression>til å angi metoden som skal startes, og med en <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeDelegateCreateExpression>til å angi metoden for å behandle hendelsen.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeDelegateCreateExpression> </xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMethodInvokeExpression>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeMethodReferenceExpression"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeMethodReferenceExpression"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeMethodReferenceExpression"></xref> class using the specified target object and method name.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeMethodReferenceExpression"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av angitte objekt og metoden målnavnet.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"></xref> that indicates the object to target.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"> </xref> som angir objektet som mål.

trans-unit.source: The name of the method to call.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på metoden for å kalle.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeMethodReferenceExpression"></xref> class using the specified target object, method name, and generic type arguments.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeMethodReferenceExpression"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av det angitte målobjektet metodenavnet og generell typeargumenter.

trans-unit.source: The `typeParameters` parameter represents a collection of type references to be substituted for the type parameter references of the current generic method.
trans-unit.target: Den `typeParameters` parameteren representerer en samling av typen referanser til erstatte refererer til parameteren typen for den gjeldende generiske metoden.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"></xref> that indicates the object to target.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"> </xref> som angir objektet som mål.

trans-unit.source: The name of the method to call.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på metoden for å kalle.

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference"></xref> values that specify the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMethodReferenceExpression.TypeArguments*> for this <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeMethodReferenceExpression"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference"> </xref> verdier som angir den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMethodReferenceExpression.TypeArguments*>for denne <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeMethodReferenceExpression"> </xref>.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMethodReferenceExpression.TypeArguments*>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the method to reference.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir navnet på metoden å referere til.

trans-unit.source: The name of the method to reference.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på metoden å referere til.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the expression that indicates the method to reference.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir uttrykket som angir metoden som skal referere til.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"></xref> that represents the method to reference.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"> </xref> som representerer metoden å referere til.

trans-unit.source: Gets the type arguments for the current generic method reference expression.
trans-unit.target: Henter typen argumentene for referanseuttrykket for gjeldende generisk metode.

trans-unit.source: The TypeArguments property represents a collection of type references to be substituted for the type parameter references of the current generic method.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen TypeArguments representerer en samling av typen referanser til erstatte refererer til parameteren typen for den gjeldende generiske metoden.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReferenceCollection"></xref> containing the type arguments for the current code <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeMethodReferenceExpression"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReferenceCollection"> </xref> som inneholder typen argumentene for den gjeldende koden <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeMethodReferenceExpression"> </xref>.
